  "detailed_description": "This is a concise horror Room escape game<br>Every time in a while, there will be terrible monsters here<br>You need to collect random items in the game and fight with them<br>And make sure your life is safe and escape<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258140/extras/61b5a9cafccede3e2dec12b261102a48.avif?t=1685186352\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br>There is a main room in the game<br>A corridor<br>3big secret rooms<br>1 small chamber<br>1 escape room<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258140/extras/1ddcd283fefbe9e57b8d21663f30b5a4.avif?t=1685186352\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br>4 kinds of monsters<br>As the time goes by, monsters will become more and more powerful<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258140/extras/afa76f6a08d2cecb2660884179cf9664.avif?t=1685186352\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br>Including more than 30 props waiting for your discovery<br>There are some random elements in the game with certain replay<br>At the same time, there are many hidden elements in the game that can help you escape<br><br>Thank you for your support",
